         RHAG 1 is comically easy to get to and kill,,,,not sure how strong your guild is but i assume  your 58-60's seeing as you need the 60spells....use 2-3 group and you will kill rhag1 fast prolly without a death or maybe 1-2.....he is located....zone in from grey...invis(yes u can invis right to him to check if he is up)...go straight up the middle hall...pass the 4 spawn to the dead end and turn LEFT.....goto the first and only right turn and open the door to an 8 spawn room.....NONE HERE SEE INVIS so relax...go into room and goto the left wall middle and there is a FAKE WALL go thru it and open door,,,,BAM there should be a rooted RHAG COMEG'ANK'Me...he has 4 lvl 54-56 Shissar Revs(SK) guards.</P><P><BR>Once we kill him Rhag2 will pop on floor 2...Rhag Mo'Goodlootz is a bit tougher but 3-4 groups(can be done with 2 groups if you need to race other guilds but some will die) will have no problem.....getting to him is way to confusing to try to type so you may need to find a map...(forgot where i got mine)....</P><P>Goodluck and may Funeral Pyre drop more often for you than it has for us.</P><P>Sallymanders<BR>Warlock of Povar<BR>Triton<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=161288">MY GEAR</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
